text: Horst Kadner (born 29 September 1930) is a German former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre pistol event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:Possibly living people Category:German male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of the United Team of Germany Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saxony
